2. Sort hollow objects by their top row position (ascending). Sort solid objects by their top row position (ascending).
3. Build output grid: width=8 (two 4×4 blocks side by side), height=4×max(num_hollow, num_solid).
4. For each row index i: left 4×4 block = i-th hollow object (or all-0 if i >= num_hollow), right 4×4 block = i-th solid object (or all-0 if i >= num_solid).
